+**Issue:** Null pointer dereference introduced when `_bfd_alloc_and_read()` was replaced by `_bfd_mmap_readonly_persistent()` in a post-2.40 refactoring
+**Impact:** Potential crash (DoS) when processing crafted ELF files on post-2.40 versions only
